# MaxMind GeoLite2 update configuration
# Get your free account + license key at: https://www.maxmind.com/en/geolite2/signup
#
# To set up on a new device:
#   1. Copy this file: cp config/GeoIP.conf.template config/GeoIP.conf
#   2. Fill in your AccountID and LicenseKey
#   3. Run: sudo geoipupdate
#
# The actual config/GeoIP.conf is gitignored (contains credentials).

AccountID YOUR_ACCOUNT_ID_HERE
LicenseKey YOUR_LICENSE_KEY_HERE

EditionIDs GeoLite2-ASN GeoLite2-City
